# XBrainLab local product configuration.
#
# The supported product path is local-first. Runtime choices are stored in
# settings.json and can be changed from the UI model settings dialog.
#
# No hosted API key is required for the default desktop workflow.
#
# Local model cache:
#   XBrainLab/llm/core/models
#
# Safe defaults:
#   active_mode = local
#   inference_mode = local
#
# Model download and health-check helpers:
#   poetry run python scripts/dev/plan_local_model_download.py --format markdown
#   poetry run python scripts/dev/inspect_local_assistant_runtime.py --format markdown
#
# Cleanup:
#   Delete unused model snapshots under XBrainLab/llm/core/models.
